snippet.title: Mega Man gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Mega Man, Dos PC game produced by Capcom in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/mega-man/5103/
Exploring, shooting and jumping through this old school platformer.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
